content:
You're welcome! I'm glad to hear it's running now. I understand your suggestion for improving efficiency - you're absolutely right. In the future, I'll ensure the artifact titles match the exact filenames with the correct extensions, so you can simply download and move the files without renaming them. This will save time and reduce the chance of file naming errors.

For example, instead of "Updated main.py (Complete File)" I'll use "main.py" as the title, making it immediately ready for use after download.

Thanks for the feedback! Is there anything else you'd like me to help with regarding your Cloud Functions setup?
